data.description: Welcome to Summergate At Stoney Creek! This Vivian plan is a graceful haven, boasts 4 large bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, offering a warm embrace to a lovely family or a soul seeking solace. The heart of this dwelling, an open kitchen, connects seamlessly to the family room. Outside, a two-car garage stands guard, while a fenced backyard and a welcoming front porch offer refuge and respite. Enjoy the sunset on the rear patio that invites you to a spacious backyard. With a timeless union of brick and stone on the front facade and granite countertops, kitchen island and kitchen backsplash give an elegant appeal, fireplace in the livingroom, this home blends elegance with functionality. Your future here is accompanied by modern conveniences, with the refrigerator, washer, and dryer included. Beyond your doorstep lies a world of opportunities - shopping, local dining, and the allure of Interstate 75, Atlanta Motor Speedway, and the retail wonderland of Fayetteville Pavilion and the Tanger Outlet. As well, enjoy nearby Lake Spivey, Lake Spivey Golf Club, and Clayton County International Park. This home isn't just a space; it's a place where your heart finds its rhythm, where your dreams take flight.
